title: relation nodes
pid: 004bf7c4-efd0-4e28-a036-06edd1616050
body: |2-
  Alternating member descriptions,
  and connecting words, where the connecting words alone
  are enough to uniquely identify the template.
  Each member description can be empty,
  in which case it is a placeholder for a member.

  After that, the relation node can have
  any arbitrary set of content,
  just like an ordinary node.
